features: KEEP PACKING ORGANIZED: BAGSMART 6 set compression packing cubes includes 1 extra large cube (11.6'' x 15.9''), 1 large cube (9.2'' x 13''), 1 medium cubes (8.2'' x 11.4''), 1 small cubes (6.5'' x 9.0''), 1 drawstring bag (13.0" x 17.7") and 1 shoe bag (9.0" x 16.9"). Different sizes can be used for different packing purposes, helping us quickly sort, organize and find our items while traveling. Say goodbye to messy suitcases and keep your clothes organized.

SAVE 60% SPACE: Just like how a vacuum sealer works. With our compression travel cubes, you can easily compress clothing and other essentials into a compact shape, freeing up to 60% of luggage space. Imagine being able to hold twice as much stuff in your luggage without compromising on style or comfort. Whether you're planning a weekend getaway or a trip around the world, our storage bags are a must-have solution for savvy travelers like you.

LIGHTWEIGHT TRAVEL ESSENTIALS: Don't let bulky suitcases cramp your style or limit your shopping opportunities. Super light fabric ensures your clothes fit neatly into your luggage without adding extra weight. These suitcase organizer bag sets are perfect when you want to reduce weight and save space in your carry-on, suitcase or backpack.

DURABLE TRAVEL ACCESSORIES: Made from premium polyester and high-density mesh, these luggage organizers can withstand daily wear and tear and are reusable, ensuring your belongings stay intact during your travels. These travel essentials packing cubes are equipped with a portable handle and sturdy two-way zippers, which are a must-have packing organizer for every trip.

WHAT WE CARE: Every traveler has their packing style preferences, and BAGSMART provides plenty of flexibility for any type of traveler. We hope to sell not just a commodity, but also a love. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just get these already!
reviews.reviewText: I am a chronic overpacker, so I got these cubes. The picture I’ve included here is the XL bag that has my big wool coat, a tunic sweater, a pair of leggings, a tank top, and a pair of undies! It is insane! It wasn’t hard to zip, either, and you don’t need any weird air compressors. I put some undergarments and a T-shirt in the smallest one. I’ve never had all my clothes fit on one side of my suitcase! Granted, I have a huge suitcase, but this is awesome! I am also not a small person, so my clothes are also not small! Haha I will probably get maybe another XL and L since I had to use one of my other packing cubes that doesn’t really compress for the clothes I’m wearing for the last day of my trip, but highly recommend these cubes!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Quality Compression Travel Cubes
reviews.reviewText: These are really good quality travel cubes!These are so handy to have for traveling. The set comes with four different compression cubes, a drawstring bag (I use it for dirty laundry), and a shoe bag. All of the compression bags work really well. They are made of a high quality material that is tear resistant which is really useful when you are trying to compress. Thick items like jeans. I don’t love the way that the drawstring bag feels and the shoe bag doesn’t work for all of my shoes but those are such small issues compared to how great this set is.The zipper pulls are good quality and the zippers easily glide. Making it much easier to compress your clothes. Perfect for organizing as well as making it easier to pack and get more space in your luggage.Overall really impressed, especially because at this price I did not expect such good quality!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars One of my all time fave Amazon purchases
reviews.reviewText: I am super impressed with these. I love that you can use with or without compression. Honestly, I crammed so much stuff in these that I expected the zippers to pop open. They didn't. At one point, I was legit sitting on one of them to compress it when I was gifted a very nice alternative down pillow 2500 miles from home--I got in there and compressed it down to a fraction of it's fluffy size. I've used packing cubes before but this is the first time I've used compression. I usually roll my clothes so many people argue that compression doesn't do much but I felt it helped a bit. I also felt my clothes were less wrinkled with these cubes. Packing was more fun with these--just watch the weight. On my last long haul, I checked 2 medium size suitcases (27 or 28 inches). One case, I had packed about ⅔ full with these cubes (one cube was my new pillow and another was a gifted throw blanket), my running shoes, 2 pairs of lightweight platform ankle boots and I was a bit over 40lbs. I'm ordering more to replace my non-compression cubes for my other case. Highly recommend to everyone!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love the dusty pink color of these packing cubes. It adds a touch of personality to my luggage. The subtle design gives this product a premium feel. It takes the dullness out of the chore of packing and makes it easy to find my belongings.The set includes six different sizes. The extra large cube is perfect for big items like sweaters, while the small cube is ideal for socks and underwear. The set also includes one shoe bag to keep one pair of shoes separate and tucked away neatly.The best thing about these packing cubes is their compression feature. With just a few simple moves, you can easily compress your clothes, saving tons of space in your luggage. You can overpack a little with no worries.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So great for travel!
reviews.reviewText: I recently had a work flight and these packing cubes were ESSENTIAL for my travel. I only took a carry-on, so it was crucial that my packing was organized, in order to help me make the best use of my small space. Having multiple size options between the different cubes helped me prioritize what items were best to bring, without letting everything mix, such as clothes with shoes. I loved these!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good sizes, love the "camel" color!
reviews.reviewText: This BAGSMART set has a good variety of bag sizes and I love the camel color. The included string bag is really cute, too. I was able to fit six pairs of women's jeans in the largest bag (folded in half and then thirds). It was an extremely tight squeeze, but I was able to zip both layers of zippers closed. It definitely felt like I was testing the seams, but they held. I love the compression of the double layer zipper system! I could probably squish loose clothes in the suitcase just as much, but this way they all stay neat and organized. The rectangular sizes fit in a 20" suitcase quite well.
